WEBVTT

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:08.681
Way before the first selfie,

00:00:08.681 --> 00:00:10.883
the ancient Greeks and Romans had a myth

00:00:10.883 --> 00:00:14.605
about someone a little too obsessed 
with his own image.

00:00:14.605 --> 00:00:15.895
In one telling,

00:00:15.895 --> 00:00:20.779
Narcissus was a handsome guy wandering
the world in search of someone to love.

00:00:20.779 --> 00:00:23.235
After rejecting a nymph named Echo,

00:00:23.235 --> 00:00:26.709
he caught a glimpse 
of his own reflection in a river,

00:00:26.709 --> 00:00:28.511
and fell in love with it.

